name: 𝕻𝖔𝖘𝖙-𝕸𝖔𝖉𝖊𝖗𝖓 𝕴𝖓𝖘𝖊𝖈𝖚𝖗𝖎𝖙𝖎𝖊𝖘
description: [Audio On]  It's all in our head, in everyone's head. Social media tend to make us feel like shit and it's not alright. Modernity, advancement in technology and bureaucratic might, progress for humanity? Doesn't feel like it. Unavoidable insecurities that make us feel like shit? feels like it.
